evals.prompt:
아래는 iced 0.12 로 짜놓은 카운터 코드다. 이걸 최신 iced 0.13 또는 0.14 스타일로 마이그레이션해줘. API 변경점(Application trait 제거, Command→Task, Appearance→Style 등) 을 반영해서 새 main.rs + Cargo.toml 을 만들어줘. 기능과 UI 는 동일하게 유지.

```rust
use iced::{Application, Command, Element, Settings, Theme, executor};
use iced::widget::{button, column, text};

pub fn main() -> iced::Result {
    Counter::run(Settings::default())
}

struct Counter { value: i64 }

#[derive(Debug, Clone, Copy)]
enum Message { Inc, Dec }

impl Application for Counter {
    type Message = Message;
    type Theme = Theme;
    type Executor = executor::Default;
    type Flags = ();

    fn new(_flags: ()) -> (Self, Command<Message>) {
        (Self { value: 0 }, Command::none())
    }
    fn title(&self) -> String { String::from("Counter") }
    fn update(&mut self, msg: Message) -> Command<Message> {
        match msg { Message::Inc => self.value += 1, Message::Dec => self.value -= 1 };
        Command::none()
    }
    fn view(&self) -> Element<'_, Message> {
        column![
            button("+").on_press(Message::Inc),
            text(self.value.to_string()).size(40),
            button("-").on_press(Message::Dec),
        ].into()
    }
    fn theme(&self) -> Theme { Theme::Dark }
}
```
